title: 134. How To Build Bulletproof Confidence
itunes:title: 134. How To Build Bulletproof Confidence
description: If you're waiting to feel more confident, you will be waiting forever. On today's episode, Andy talks about where real confidence comes from, debunks the idea that people are born with confidence, and tells you the steps you need to take to build the confidence you desire.
